Definition: Biblicist is a Born Again Christian who believes in man's total depravity (that man cant save himself), in Unmerited Favor, that man can limit atonement, that man can resist the call of the Holy Spirit, believes in Christ's substitutionary death, and in the Preservation of Saints. They also believe in the Biblical Gospel of salvation."

